{"id": "1398700656809869494", "channel_id": "1398620009898708992", "type": 0, "author_id": "364412673275723779", "author_name": "zier.0", "author_bot": false, "content": "By the way, what is up with the Tulu Over-Exalt change?\n\nIt is completely ignorant of how people play Tulu nowadays.\n\nFirst of all, all this time, Tulu's Over-Exalt *was* and has always been AoE, it's been tested and tried, and I have video evidence to prove it. Do the developers of Morimens not play their own game? Why would this be clarified otherwise?\n\nSecond, Tulu's Over-Exalt kills any form of creativity with the ability. One such case (and is personal to me), is that Tulu would clear out any mobs in the way, before Corposant would use her 4-cost card to burst the boss down. Another case was during the 1.5 Anniversary raid event, wherein Tulu cleared all the mobs immediately and allowed people to burst the boss directly, leading to extremely fast clear times. Seeing Tulu's potential really fascinated me. Now Tulu is just downgraded to \"end of turn tentacle archetype\" that you're trying to push and in my opinion it's honestly boring.\n\nThird, Tulu's Over-Exalt was a very reliable way to stack his Soulforge Aptitude during critical turns. Now, you have to either play his 4-cost or spend resources stacking it, so that other Tentacle Damage scaling Awakeners can make use of it. This just feels more clunky, and it reduces the effectiveness of Tulu's synergies with other Awakeners. \n\nPlease change it back or at least, give players the option to activate either the previous or the new effect.", "timestamp": "2025-07-26T16:17:03.185000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 14}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398620009898708992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.0.2 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1398701760247369788", "channel_id": "1398620009898708992", "type": 0, "author_id": "364412673275723779", "author_name": "zier.0", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://youtu.be/gi2IxjfXP7Q?t=84\n\nVideo evidence of Tulu Over-Exalt being already AoE. Timestamp is included in the link.", "timestamp": "2025-07-26T16:21:26.265000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "[Morimens] STR Steal Shenanigans | Arc 2 H1-9 Deathless (w/ Corposa...", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gi2IxjfXP7Q&start=84", "description": "BGM source: https://youtu.be/GNOSWb9uO0k?si=hEDocutSiSkwX6re\n\nI thought this one was funny enough to share - also tried a bit of editing in some comments?\n\nCredits to Anna."}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398620009898708992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.0.2 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1398744092950663318", "channel_id": "1398620009898708992", "type": 0, "author_id": "484555315447332864", "author_name": "randomplayer852", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家在意的還是這個皮膚放禮包的問題。\n從給的抽數這個角度上來說皮膚更像是一個贈品，對我來說也是如此。有沒有這個皮膚這個禮包我也會買。但是就是會有不少更在乎皮膚的人。對那些人來說這個皮膚就會是付費的。而事實上要拿到這個皮膚就是要花錢。既然如此。花錢的皮膚就應該和先前的簡約換裝有所區別。貓你自己也說的簡約換裝的初心就是讓一些製作組的一些作品不被埋沒，也認可了這次是考慮不周，那麼有沒有什麼優化皮膚獲取方式的改動呢？\n即使是這次因為更新包已經做好了不方便改，那有沒有對於未來 不會再把簡約換裝 放進付費內容的承諾呢？\n說實話會買這個禮包不給這個皮膚也會買，因為給的抽數就是相對比較值的。不會去買的我不認為就會因為這個皮膚選擇買了。為了這個挨罵我覺得實屬沒必要。", "timestamp": "2025-07-26T19:09:39.168000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "thumbsup", "emoji_id": "1356086340298473574", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398620009898708992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.0.2 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1398745690846396537", "channel_id": "1398620009898708992", "type": 0, "author_id": "484555315447332864", "author_name": "randomplayer852", "author_bot": false, "content": "圖魯的改動在我這裡是機制上的優化。因為圖魯超限一直吃不到船長的buff不說，回合外被觸手拍死結束戰鬥也能多回一次狂氣和銀鑰。\n\n能給一個選擇讓大家決定發動的時機肯定是更好的，除非你能保證這個改動在絕大部分的情況下是正收益。不過從英文區的玩家的角度上看，似乎更傾向是削弱的樣子。🤔", "timestamp": "2025-07-26T19:16:00.136000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398620009898708992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.0.2 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
